    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024160/extras/095758e3af41e9dd6742ad4cb693bd46.avif?t=1771344984\" width=790 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在近未来的纽约市，城市的地铁系统已经分裂为多个相互对立的区域，每个区域都由一位铁道巨头掌控：他们是拥有大量忠实拥趸的明星驾驶员，拥有充裕的资金，并对自己所在的线路拥有绝对的掌控权。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>但很可惜，你并不是他们中的一员。</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">你名下只有一辆老旧的破火车，毫无声望，想要受人尊重更是痴心妄想。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024160/extras/dd816a322a359ad187a38dffc3045e3c.poster.avif?t=1771344984\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024160/extras/dd816a322a359ad187a38dffc3045e3c.webm?t=1771344984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024160/extras/dd816a322a359ad187a38dffc3045e3c.mp4?t=1771344984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">想要飞黄腾达，光靠速度可是不够的。接取任务、赚取金钱、扩大粉丝群体，还有逐步积累声望，进而将这些领地纳入囊中——一次一条线路。小心行事，随便飙车可能会害得你失去手中的一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>智胜你的对手。挑战铁道巨头。夺取他们的地盘。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024160/extras/9ca3fd829d10f19a80d6a615eca66779.poster.avif?t=1771344984\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024160/extras/9ca3fd829d10f19a80d6a615eca66779.webm?t=1771344984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024160/extras/9ca3fd829d10f19a80d6a615eca66779.mp4?t=1771344984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>这将是一场赌上代价的竞速。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">《地铁劲敌》（Metro Rivals）是一款融合了策略竞速、轻度模拟与故事驱动的独特游戏。只有深谋远虑的玩家才能脱颖而出，那些只会把油门踩到底的冲动之辈可无法笑到最后。</p>",
